high_descs: Turn left and go the the small black table against the wall, near the piano.
Pick up the set of keys nearest the center of the table.
Face the opposite direction and go to the left side of the ottoman, then turn to face it.
Place the keys on the ottoman, near the closest edge and to the right of the bolster.
Face left, then go around the ottoman to face the left side of the chair near the ottoman.
Pick up the set of keys from the seat of the chair.
Return to where you placed the first keys on the ottoman.
Place the second set of keys to the right of the first set.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys on an ottoman.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk through the living room, to the black end table, between the piano and the couch.
Pick up the keys on the black end table, between the other set of keys and the vase.
Turn around and go to the ottoman, in front of the chair that is beside the piano.
Place the keys on the ottoman, to the right of the pillow.
Turn to your left and go around the ottoman, to the left side of the chair in front of it.
Pick up the keys on the cushion of the chair to the right of the credit card.
Turn to your right and go back around the ottoman so that you are facing the front of the chair again.
Place the keys on the ottoman, between the pillows and the other set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the ottoman.
